Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,20,,Did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,20,,And have you seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Those two shockingly beautiful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,Overflowing with startling romance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,All-consuming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,Inescapable
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,20,,With a Taishou Era charming lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
