Comment: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP end}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a Hikaru Genji or just a Narihira? {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ariwara_no_Narihira - not sure what's the allusion, probably because Narihira was a Casanova}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The super handsome second lieutenant receives mountains of love letters every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But among them, there is one from a woman \Nwhom Shinobu is dating regularly, in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wishing for nothing more than to protect our High Collar Lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,these two conspire to tail Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But because their mission is to be kept secret from Benio, Ushigorou fails his assignment,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and so she stumbles across\NShinobu's date herself, in all her glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she a fool for being so trusting? \NOr is the deceiving side in the wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady can't sleep. \NWhen will the truth come to light?{ちょっぴり眠れのハイカラさんこの真相は いつ晴れる}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This affliction goes way deeper than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do something about it...{なんとかしなくちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bummer that we have to wake up before everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough, isn't it?{辛いわよねー}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure it's for a reason \Nthat they say "the early bird gets the worm." {lit: I'm sure something good will happen to us one of these days - nothing of sorts happens later so idk why this line is here}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?{何かしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Ranko exercising.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. \NLet's ask her to train us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you teach us to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought it was Ranko...{蘭子さんだとばっかり}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.{いいのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, wanna try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a good workout \Nto wash your worries away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:04:00.45,Sign,,0,0,150,,{\c&HEBE2E7&\b1\blur1.001\bord0}Episode 21 \N {\fs80.001} Life is Short, Yet Riddled with Worries {命みじかく悩み果てなく}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks delicious. \NBenio will surely like it.{おいしそう、Benioさん喜ぶの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?{なんと}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Benio has been working out since early morning, so she'll definitely be very hungry.{お腹を減らしてるに違いないんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.{おはようございます }
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is looking to be another \Nespecially pleasant morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can already feel \Nthe heavy stomach and the heartburn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, you aren't eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it away. \NI don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But breakfast is important for your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.{いいのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's wrong, Benio?{どうしたのじゃあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, you'd down three bowls of rice first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you perchance eat something bad \Nwhile scavenging?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Hate to break it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but even I have periods when I'm simply not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I'm so mad!{イライラする}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be in a rather ill humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm! This might just be an omen of an incoming cataclysm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope it's not an earthquake, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you joke so casually \Nabout Benio's condition?! {no clue what's namazu here and without it the rest doesn't make sense either}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You should all be seriously worried for her instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure wonder what actually happened to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For all he's worth, I'm not supposed \Nto give a diddly damn about him... {not sure what she means}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the reason I lost my appetite.{食欲減退イライラの原因が歩いてきたわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You do know going to school without eating is unhealthy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you at least drink some milk for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs200\pos(396.68,56.89)\bord2\blur2}Boom!{ドカー}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,L-L-Leave me alone please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't keep my cool \Nwhen I see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone! \NI don't wanna see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to have fallen into her disfavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It really hurts my pride.{/confidence}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met a girl so cold to me. {lit: without popularity (maybe "unmoved by my charms")}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though I've always been serious about my feelings, we didn't grow any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been a while \Nsince I first met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter what I do, \Nthat bird keeps flying further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, it's finally time to go to school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At your service!{合点承知}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you should leave without eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all good.{へいきよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! You've done your homework, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I didn't, that doesn't matter right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leaving this place for a while \Nwould be good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I meet up with all of my classmates again, \NI'll cheer up in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go.{さやってよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:07:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be in very bad shape.{なんだかひどく参ってるみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried... What should I do?{心配だなどうしよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, I'm going out too,\Nso let's ride together 'till the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hell no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you go any faster?{もっと早く走れないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to speed up. \NDidn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just sayin', they call me Supersonic Ushigorou, \Nso try not to fly away!{no clue what's jimannoko here and what he means in the last part}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou! Faster! Don't slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So she is avoiding me. But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ride along Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my intention, \Nbut with the power of loathing, she broke away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you following after her, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I did that, I'd only end up \Nhurting her even more instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!{噓}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was me, I'd put my life on the line, \Nand follow the person I love to the end of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Benio \Nwas hoping that you'd chase her.{Benioさんも きっと少尉が追ってくるのを待っていた はずなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't understand such a simple thing,\Nyou don't deserve your playboy title.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep down, Benio...{benioさんの心の中は}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks about nothing but you.{心の中はshouiのことでいっぱいなのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...{だから}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she's pushing you away \Nwith her words!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't understand even such a simple thing, hands off Benio!{benioさんから手を引いて}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot... Idiot...\NUshigorou, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Didja say somethin' to me, Boss?{親分なんかおっしゃいましたか}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you actually go faster \Nwhen I told you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eck! I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I always follow your orders, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why would I not want \Nto ride side by side with Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you command me to speed up, then? {nc whats ganshou here}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... Why would you necessarily run faster \Njust 'cause someone tells you to? {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Didja want me to go faster, after all? \NOr did that mean I should slow down? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye! It ain't make no sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You thickheaded henchman.\NHyaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I get it!{わかりました}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have {\i1}that thing{\i0} for Shinobu!{/the L-word}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, how could I? {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it's you, teach!{あら、先生}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it, \Nwe've not seen you in a long while indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why I feel \Nlike I've missed y'all so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura says she missed me? \NThis can't be a good omen. Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,200)\c&H292922&\3c&HE0E7DB&}Righteous path towards wifehood
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope nothing bad happens today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone!{おはよう、皆様}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ages!{お久しぶり}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you must be so busy you have no time at all to go to school these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I've got a lot on my plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I'm finally here, \Nlet's celebrate it with some anmitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so sorry, but I'll have to go \Nstraight home after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why so?{ほらどうした}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Osono needs to prepare for her official wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not just me. Kanoko too.{でも私だけじゃないのよKanokoさんも}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Otei too.{I think it's Otei...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there are also Shizuko and Matsuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we can't spare any time for anmitsu right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Osono, when will they hold the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, before asking others, \Nwhy don't you let us know about your own one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen, who do you think \Nis gonna get married first?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Probably Shizuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be Kanoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't forget Matsuya!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.22,0:13:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's obviously Shizuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:22.22,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000100&\fade(1450,450)\b0\blur1.001\3c&HCF6111&\org(740,523)\frz200\t(\frz450)}Wow-wow
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:22.22,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000100&\fade(1450,450)\b0\blur1.001\3c&HCF6111&\org(740,523)\frz250\t(\frz500)} Chitter-chatter {honestly, no clue what's this ぺ／ワ４わ／ね／か thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:22.22,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000100&\fade(1450,450)\b0\blur1.001\3c&HCF6111&\org(740,523)\frz300\t(\frz550)} Kyaa Kyaa Kyaa!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuya for sure!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance! {no idea}
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After not coming to school for just a short while, \Nn-now I feel like I've been left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:30.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000100&\fade(0,0)\fs70\b0\blur1.001\3c&HCD5D0F&\frz23.83\pos(455.45,430.4)} Left out {solitarily; in a lonely fashion; all alone; by oneself}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How miserable...{みじめ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for all of us to decide our path.{みんな進路が決まっていく時期なのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll graduate soon, after all.{もうすぐ女学校も卒業ですもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that long face?\NAren't you getting married to Ijuuin yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it mean that Benio's marriage talks were the first to be concluded?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! It was her!{よそうだったんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:03.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H332B1C&\fs120\b1\bord1\blur1.001\c&HD2D7D0&}Wifehood {the same word as on the sign}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, one more thing I'd like to talk about\Nbefore checking your homework today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Since many of you are brides-to-be by now, \NI'd like to give you some advice {/with the day of your marriage drawing near,}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,regarding your choice of the woman's path.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,May I, Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Kobayashi?{小林さんなんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am! While your academic advice \Non our womanly duties could indeed prove invaluable,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't it be more beneficial for us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to listen to the first-hand account of the married life, \Ngrounded in one's actual experience of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm all for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want a firsthand account, \Ngrounded in experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,y-you're out of luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I devoted my life to teaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so even in my age, being unmarried,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the position to advise you on the matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we clear?! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Teacher, you shouldn't take this personally. {/don't feel inferior/jealous}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:15:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I wasn't asking you, seeing as we have an engaged bride in this very class, {not sure what she means by "I gave up on sensei"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,who already lives at her husband-to-be's house
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and is an unrivaled expert in the matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right, I see. \NWell, then...{なるほどそれで}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! We'd all like to hear Benio \Nrecount her firsthand experience vividly to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, tell us more!{べにお聞かせて}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura, please let everyone make use \Nof your valuable experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm... I... I...{あの私あたし}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you address your future husband? {meaning "dear/honey"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you held hands yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you kissed yet? \NMwah, mwah!{接吻}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Why won't the ever-vigorous Miss Hanamura \Ntell us about how her life is these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's an order!{いいえ、命令です}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I really have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax and speak already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, tell us.{べにお、言ってよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki? Why are you interested in it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I believe, I have every right to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand why, don't you?{わかるでしょこのように}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, go on now.{さあおっしゃって}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I'll be perfectly honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!{早く}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, in regards \Nto the personal experience I could share,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:52.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\c&HE5DDE5&\3c&H181E16&\b1\fax0.179096\fscx160.33\fscy113.17\frz-0.5395\frx4.2947\fry6.8691\xbord1.54\ybord1.53\org(565.92,380.57)\pos(558.74,352.28)}Tailoring Club
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Shinobu is seeing a geisha?{忍さんの芸者と}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...{信じられないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:08.01,Song,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the Sumida River of spring’s freshness{\i0} {can't believe I found this song by listening to a poppuri of "songs about spring for children" since that's the only word I could get here and it fucking worked: https://douyo-shouka.com/hana/}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this can't be right. Shinobu loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I even spotted them going out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She writes him letters too. It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:18.67,Song,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boatmen come and go with the tides{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Would I be crying this much if it was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Benio, \Nyou still love Shinobu, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:28.80,Song,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Drops from their oars scatter like blossoms{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance! I'll never like him!{違うわそんなはずないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar. Look at this liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you be so upset if you hated him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those tears and the stubborn denial \Ngive you away at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:39.56,Song,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should one make of this scene?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My best friend sees through me, \Nas is to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, the one Shinobu loves is that geisha.{でもしょういが好きなのはその芸者さんなのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You loved him too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, aren't you shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, speaking of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already let go of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki...{たまき}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to live in doubt forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After graduation, I wanna try working.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Living on my own, as a new woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, find myself a new love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Short is the life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall in love, maidens...{命短し恋せよ乙女 - a poem}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki is bouncy as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She's moved on without a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, we might end up \Nwalking different paths after this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but may we both find the way to happiness \Nwith our own efforts. {/build with our own hands}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll forget that I've ever met
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that dumbass lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go again...{またそんなこと言って}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something \Nyou got wrong about that geisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I know what kind of person Shinobu is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She really does know Shinobu better than I do in every regard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so miserable...{私してみじめ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go the opposite way.{ 反対の方へやって}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Aren't you goin' home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions. Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The road to the Ijuuin mansion is to the left, \Nbut she went to the right, which is very suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As a teacher, I cannot let this slide.{教師としてほっとおけん}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait, rickshaw. I need a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.{へいへい}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up now! \NChase after that rickshaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Chase?{尾行}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not a very nice thing to do...{nc what he means by odayaka here}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop objecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:19:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!{早く}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Make haste!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Make haste!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you run any more energetically?\NDo your trademark "here I go" or something?! {arayotto}{one big guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, if you keep complaining while sitting up there, dangling your legs, nobody is going to serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're in that much of a hurry, \Nwhy don't you do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You lowlife, you dare patronize a woman?{no clue whats adadotte}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's switch then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.52,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(00,0)\bord1.999\c&HEAE4E7&\3c&H0E163C&\blur1.001\t(0,500,\fs200)\pos(734,606)} Bonk {ボカッ - bop; pow; bonk; thump}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I run you over, you're dead!{personalised}\NMake way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what was that? {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder. \NWild rickshaw, maybe? {/bosozoku}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn right on the next intersection.{その先を右へ廻って}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to Yanagibashi.{柳橋をやってちょうだい}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:20:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagibashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, wanna get even with those Violet Band dudes, Boss?{柳橋あああのすみれ組に殴り込みでしか親分 - they appeared in episode 14 *I think* - the one in which Kichiji first appears}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell are we goin', then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To a geisha house, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! Fooling with geishas \Nain't somethin' a woman should do!{芸者遊びなんて女のするこっちゃ誤算せん ぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it to you, \Nwho doesn't see me as a woman anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!{あばよっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:36.01,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.285563\bord1\blur1\fscx65.14\fscy88.93\frz-17.6136\frx-11.0762\fry18.6658\xbord2.66\ybord3.56\org(792.32,473.06)\pos(787.67,450.83)\c&H2A2837&\3c&H7D9DC7&}House of Flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be going now.{行ってくるわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha, Boss! Take your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,V-Visiting a geisha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...{信じられない}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be hallucinating...\NA geisha...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,May I come in?{失礼いたします}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle is about to begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,With how progressive our High Collar Lady is, \Ncan fooling around with geishas as a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,be considered a mere vagary, \Nor is she going too far after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Face to face, the two are as different as day and night. {花は紅柳は緑 - wordplay on the proverb 柳は緑花は紅 - Hana-> Hanamura, Yanagi->Yanagibashi; "The willows are green and the flowers are red" - used to say how different things are but that is a natural way of things}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The knives are out in the red light district tonight,\Nas the two women clash in a decisive battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,High Collar Lady decides that tonight is the night \Nto clarify her relationship with Shinobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so she asks Kichiji to marry Shinobu herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.47,0:23:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This turns into a heated woman-to-woman battle \Nwhere love is at stake. {女と女の戦いは汁は暇なかこいのいじ.. can't understand... - same after tatakai but fuck this show and fuck this narrator and his stupid previews}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But what do you know - Kichiji stuns Benio \Nwith her astonishing life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See in the next episode of {\i1}Here comes the High Collar Lady:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Falling Flowers, Blooming Flowers and Flowers of Love."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:21.39,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 22 \NFalling Flowers, Blooming Flowers and Flowers of Love {散る花咲く花恋の花}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Comment: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED start}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.83,Default,,0,0,20,,Just a tomboyish lady who's a little pretentious
